# Keep the build context lean for docker builds at the repo root.
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.github
**/README.md
**/*.md
!CLAUDE.md

# .NET build artifacts
**/bin
**/obj
artifacts/
coverage/
TestResults/

# Node / Angular
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.angular
**/.cache

# Editor
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea

# Env files — never baked into images
.env
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Design bundle (reference only, not needed at build time)
design/

# Compose artifacts
.docker-data/
